Ruby LLSD library
-----------------
    v1 - 2010-06-09 - Joshua Linden (Joshua Bell)

ABOUT
=====
This library implements LLSD in Ruby. It represents most LLSD types as their
native Ruby equivalents:


LLSD Type          Ruby Type
------------------ ---------------
Undefined          NilClass
Boolean            TrueClass, FalseClass
Integer            Integer, FixNum
Real               Float
String             String
Date               Date, DateTime
URI                String
UUID               String
Binary             String (base64 encoded)
Array              Array
Map                Hash

Only XML serialization is supported.


DEPENDENCIES
============

The following modules from the Ruby Stnadard Libray are required:
* test/unit
* rexml/document
* date


RUNNING TESTS
=============
You can run the unit tests on the command line:

    ruby test/llsd_test.rb
